<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Valorización Industrial Circular · Alimentación y Bebidas · Dossier Surus 2026</title>
<meta name="description" content="Valorización industrial circular en Alimentación y Bebidas: 17 casos verificados de desimplantación y segunda vida de activos. Datos literales del PDF oficial Surus.">
<meta name="keywords" content="valorización industrial, desimplantación circular, segunda vida activos, economía circular industrial, Alimentación y Bebidas, sector A&B, subastas industriales, Escrapalia, Surus">
<meta property="og:title" content="Valorización industrial circular · 17 casos A&B verificados · Dossier Surus 2026">
<meta property="og:description" content="Cada activo industrial encuentra su siguiente destino. 17 casos verificados de Alimentación y Bebidas, datos literales del PDF oficial Surus.">
<meta property="og:type" content="article">
<meta property="og:url" content="https://alimentos-ten.vercel.app/SURUS-Alimentacion-Bebidas-2026">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..144,300;0,9..144,400;0,9..144,500;0,9..144,600;1,9..144,300;1,9..144,400;1,9..144,500&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  /* === TOKENS · MODO CLARO === */
  :root {
    /* Surfaces */
    --bg-deep:      #FFFFFF;
    --bg-elev-1:    #FAF8F3;   /* off-white cálido */
    --bg-elev-2:    #F1ECE0;   /* card sutil */
    --bg-tint:      #F5F1E8;   /* tinte cálido para bloques */
    --line-fine:    #E4DED0;   /* separador fino */
    --line-strong:  #C8BFA8;   /* separador fuerte */
    /* Textos (validados WCAG AA sobre #FFFFFF) */
    --ink-primary:  #0E1F26;   /* grafito teal oscuro · 16.9:1 */
    --ink-body:     #2D2D2D;   /* grafito cuerpo · 13.8:1 */
    --ink-muted:    #717171;   /* gris labels · 4.88:1 */
    --ink-faint:    #9A9A9A;   /* gris muy suave */
    /* Brand */
    --brand:        #106070;   /* teal oficial Surus · 7.17:1 */
    --brand-hi:     #1A7A8A;   /* teal claro para hover */
    --brand-lo:     #0A4A56;   /* teal profundo */
    --bronze:       #B08A52;   /* SOLO ornamentos/numeros · 3.18:1 (no texto) */
    --bronze-hi:    #C9A36B;
    --bronze-lo:    #7A5E38;
    --olive:        #6B8E4F;   /* sage profundo · OK sobre blanco */
    --sage:         #8A9A5B;
    --serif-italic: #5A6B5A;   /* verde sage oscuro para italicas */
    --signal-warn:  #B85A1F;   /* naranja profundo */

    --display: 'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
    --sans: 'Inter', -apple-system, 'SF Pro Display', system-ui, sans-serif;
    --mono: 'JetBrains Mono', Menlo, monospace;

    --gutter: clamp(24px, 4vw, 80px);
    --max-w: 1440px;

    --ease-out: cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
    --ease-quart: cubic-bezier(0.25, 1, 0.5, 1);
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html {
    scroll-snap-type: y mandatory;
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
    background: var(--bg-deep);
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }
  body {
    background: var(--bg-deep);
    color: var(--ink-body);
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 450;
    line-height: 1.55;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
  }

  /* Atmospheric grain (detrás de TODO, no afecta contenido ni imágenes) */
  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed; inset: 0;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg viewBox='0 0 200 200' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'><filter id='n'><feTurbulence baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='2' seed='5'/><feColorMatrix values='0 0 0 0 0.55  0 0 0 0 0.45  0 0 0 0 0.30  0 0 0 0.10 0'/></filter><rect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)'/></svg>");
    opacity: 0.4;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: -1;
  }

  /* === HEADER (transparente, no tapa nada) === */
  .topbar {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 200;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    padding: 22px var(--gutter);
    background: transparent;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .topbar > * { pointer-events: auto; }
  .brand {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-primary);
    display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: center;
  }
  .brand .dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; background: var(--brand); border-radius: 50%; }
  .counter {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  }
  .counter b {
    color: var(--ink-primary);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }
  .progress-line {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--bronze-lo) 0%, var(--bronze) 50%, var(--bronze-hi) 100%);
    z-index: 250;
    width: 0%;
    transition: width 100ms linear;
  }

  /* === NAV DOTS === */
  .nav-dots {
    position: fixed; right: 28px; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%);
    z-index: 150;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px;
  }
  .nav-dot {
    width: 8px; height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--line-strong);
    border: 0;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 280ms var(--ease-out);
    padding: 0;
  }
  .nav-dot:hover { background: var(--ink-muted); transform: scale(1.3); }
  .nav-dot.active { background: var(--brand); transform: scale(1.8); }

  /* === BOTONES DE NAVEGACIÓN VISIBLES === */
  .nav-btn {
    position: fixed; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%);
    z-index: 160;
    width: 52px; height: 52px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #FFFFFF;
    border: 1px solid var(--line-strong);
    color: var(--ink-primary);
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(14, 31, 38, 0.08), 0 1px 2px rgba(14, 31, 38, 0.04);
    transition: all 220ms var(--ease-out);
    padding: 0;
  }
  .nav-btn:hover {
    background: var(--brand);
    color: #FFFFFF;
    border-color: var(--brand);
    transform: translateY(-50%) scale(1.06);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(16, 96, 112, 0.18);
  }
  .nav-btn:active { transform: translateY(-50%) scale(0.96); }
  .nav-btn:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid var(--brand);
    outline-offset: 4px;
  }
  .nav-btn:disabled,
  .nav-btn.is-disabled {
    opacity: 0.3;
    cursor: not-allowed;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .nav-btn-prev { left: 28px; }
  .nav-btn-next { right: 28px; }
  .nav-btn svg { width: 20px; height: 20px; display: block; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .nav-btn { width: 44px; height: 44px; }
    .nav-btn-prev { left: 12px; }
    .nav-btn-next { right: 12px; }
    .nav-btn svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; }
  }

  /* === SLIDES === */
  .slide {
    min-height: 100vh;
    min-height: 100svh;
    scroll-snap-align: start;
    scroll-snap-stop: always;
    padding: clamp(60px, 7vh, 90px) var(--gutter) clamp(50px, 5vh, 80px);
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line-fine);
    z-index: 2;
  }
  .slide-inner {
    max-width: var(--max-w);
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
  }

  /* Reveal animations on scroll */
  .reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(32px); transition: opacity 900ms var(--ease-out), transform 900ms var(--ease-out); }
  .reveal.in, .no-js .reveal { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  .reveal[data-delay="1"] { transition-delay: 100ms; }
  .reveal[data-delay="2"] { transition-delay: 200ms; }
  .reveal[data-delay="3"] { transition-delay: 300ms; }
  .reveal[data-delay="4"] { transition-delay: 400ms; }
  .reveal[data-delay="5"] { transition-delay: 500ms; }
  .reveal[data-delay="6"] { transition-delay: 600ms; }

  /* === TYPE === */
  .kicker {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--bronze);
    letter-spacing: 0.32em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
  }
  .kicker::before {
    content: ''; width: 28px; height: 1px; background: var(--bronze);
  }
  h1.display {
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 72px);
    line-height: 1.02;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    color: var(--ink-primary);
    font-style: normal;
  }
  h1.display em { color: var(--brand); font-style: italic; font-weight: 500; }
  h2.display {
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: clamp(28px, 3.8vw, 56px);
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--ink-primary);
  }
  h2.display em { color: var(--brand); font-style: italic; font-weight: 500; }
  h2.display u {
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--bronze);
    padding-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .lede {
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(16px, 1.2vw, 20px);
    line-height: 1.45;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    max-width: 64ch;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }
  .micro {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* === SLIDE 01 · COVER === */
  .portada-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.15fr 1fr;
    gap: clamp(40px, 6vw, 100px);
    align-items: center;
  }
  .portada-img-wrap {
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 5/6;
    max-height: 78vh;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--bg-elev-1);
  }
  .portada-img-wrap img {
    width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;
    filter: contrast(1.08) saturate(0.78) brightness(0.92);
    transition: transform 1.2s var(--ease-out);
  }
  .slide.in .portada-img-wrap img { transform: scale(1.0); }
  .portada-img-wrap::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(11,12,16,0) 50%, rgba(11,12,16,0.55) 100%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .auth-caption {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 18px; left: 18px;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--ink-primary);
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    background: rgba(11,12,16,0.7);
    backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
    padding: 7px 12px;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--bronze);
    z-index: 3;
  }
  .auth-caption::before {
    content: ''; display: inline-block; width: 5px; height: 5px;
    background: var(--bronze); border-radius: 50%;
    margin-right: 9px; vertical-align: middle;
  }
  .portada-meta {
    display: flex; gap: 10px; margin-top: 24px; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .badge {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 7px 11px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line-fine);
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .badge.gold { color: var(--bronze-hi); border-color: var(--bronze); }
  .badge.olive { color: var(--olive); border-color: var(--olive); }
  .cta-top {
    margin-top: 28px;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    color: var(--ink-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.28em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 10px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--bronze);
    align-self: flex-start;
    transition: gap 240ms var(--ease-out), color 240ms;
  }
  .cta-top:hover { gap: 18px; color: var(--brand); }
  .cta-top::after { content: '↓'; }

  /* === SLIDE 02 · 17 CASOS BENTO === */
  .bento {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr);
    grid-auto-rows: 96px;
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--line-fine);
    border: 1px solid var(--line-fine);
    margin-top: 32px;
  }
  .bento-cell {
    background: var(--bg-deep);
    padding: 18px 16px;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between;
    transition: background 280ms;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .bento-cell:hover { background: var(--bg-elev-1); }
  .bento-cell.lg { grid-column: span 3; grid-row: span 2; }
  .bento-cell.md { grid-column: span 2; grid-row: span 2; }
  .bento-cell.sm { grid-column: span 2; }
  .bento-n {
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--bronze);
    line-height: 1;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .bento-cell.lg .bento-n { font-size: 52px; }
  .bento-name {
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink-primary);
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .bento-cell.lg .bento-name { font-size: 19px; margin-top: 6px; }
  .bento-loc {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 8px;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 3px;
  }
  .bento-tag {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 8px;
    color: var(--bronze);
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 8px;
    padding-top: 8px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line-fine);
  }
  .bento-cell.lg .bento-tag { font-size: 9px; }

  /* === SLIDE 03 · DOLORES === */
  .dolores-wrap {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.6fr;
    gap: clamp(40px, 5vw, 80px);
    align-items: start;
    margin-top: 32px;
  }
  .dolores-pull {
    position: sticky; top: 120px;
  }
  .dolores-pull blockquote {
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-size: clamp(22px, 2.2vw, 32px);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: var(--ink-primary);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .dolores-pull blockquote::before {
    content: '"';
    font-size: 64px;
    color: var(--bronze);
    line-height: 0;
    vertical-align: -20px;
    margin-right: 4px;
  }
  .dolores-pull .attr {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }
  .dolores-list {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line-fine);
  }
  .dolor {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 50px 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
    padding: 16px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line-fine);
    align-items: baseline;
  }
  .dolor-n {
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--bronze);
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .dolor-content h3 {
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-size: 19px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink-primary);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .dolor-content p {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
  }

  /* === SLIDE 04 · SOLUCION === */
  .sol-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--line-fine);
    border: 1px solid var(--line-fine);
    margin-top: 32px;
  }
  .sol-cell {
    background: var(--bg-deep);
    padding: 28px 24px;
    min-height: 320px;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between;
    transition: background 320ms;
  }
  .sol-cell:hover { background: var(--bg-elev-1); }
  .sol-num {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--bronze);
    letter-spacing: 0.32em;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .sol-name {
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--ink-primary);
    margin-top: 14px;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }
  .sol-desc {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    margin-top: 16px;
  }
  .sol-out {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--bronze);
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 28px;
    padding-top: 18px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line-fine);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* === SLIDE 04 · SOLUCION             -->
  /* === SLIDE 05 · METODOLOGÍA TIMELINE === */
  .metodo-wrap {
    margin-top: 32px;
  }
  .metodo-title {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--bronze);
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
  }
  .metodo-title::before { content: 'FASE 1 · CORE'; color: var(--bronze-hi); }
  .metodo-flow {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr);
    gap: 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line-fine);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line-fine);
  }
  .met-step {
    padding: 28px 18px;
    border-right: 1px solid var(--line-fine);
    text-align: left;
    position: relative;
  }
  .met-step:last-child { border-right: 0; }
  .met-n {
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--bronze);
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1;
    display: block;
  }
  .met-t {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 12px;
  }
  .met-step::after {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute; right: -10px; top: 50%;
    color: var(--bronze); font-size: 18px;
    transform: translateY(-50%); z-index: 2;
  }
  .met-step:last-child::after { content: ''; }

  .metodo-flow.bonus { border-top: 0; background: var(--bg-elev-1); }
  .metodo-flow.bonus .met-n { color: var(--olive); }
  .metodo-flow.bonus .met-step::after { color: var(--olive); }
  .metodo-title.bonus::before { content: 'FASE 2 · CONTINUIDAD'; color: var(--olive); }

  /* === METODOLOGÍA · ICONOS SVG === */
  .met-ico {
    width: 38px; height: 38px;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    color: var(--bronze);
    stroke: currentColor;
    fill: none;
    stroke-width: 1.5;
    stroke-linecap: round;
    stroke-linejoin: round;
    transition: transform 220ms ease, color 220ms ease, stroke-width 220ms ease;
  }
  .metodo-flow.bonus .met-ico { color: var(--olive); }
  .met-step:hover .met-ico { transform: translateY(-2px); stroke-width: 1.8; }
  .met-step { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
  .met-step .met-ico { margin-bottom: 16px; }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .met-ico { width: 32px; height: 32px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  }
  @media (hover: none) {
    .met-step:hover .met-ico { transform: none; stroke-width: 1.5; }
  }

  /* === SLIDE 06 · TRACK RECORD · CHARTS === */
  .tr-wrap {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;
    gap: clamp(40px, 5vw, 80px);
    margin-top: 48px;
  }
  .tr-metrics { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
  .tr-m {
    padding: 14px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line-fine);
  }
  .tr-m-v {
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-size: clamp(32px, 3.6vw, 48px);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--bronze);
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }
  .tr-m-l {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .tr-charts { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 32px; }

  /* Donut */
  .donut-wrap { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 24px; }
  .donut-svg { flex-shrink: 0; }
  .donut-legend { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; flex: 1; }
  .donut-legend-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink-muted); }
  .donut-legend-row .swatch { width: 10px; height: 10px; flex-shrink: 0; border-radius: 1px; }
  .donut-legend-row b { color: var(--ink-primary); font-weight: 500; margin-left: auto; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }

  /* Bars */
  .bars-title { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; color: var(--ink-faint); letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .tr-bar {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 100px 1fr 40px;
    align-items: center; gap: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .tr-bar-l {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .tr-bar-bg {
    height: 5px; background: var(--line-fine); position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .tr-bar-fg {
    position: absolute; left: 0; top: 0; height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--bronze-lo) 0%, var(--bronze-hi) 100%);
    width: 0;
    transition: width 1400ms var(--ease-quart);
  }
  .tr-bar-v {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--ink-primary);
    text-align: right;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }

  /* === MAPA ESPAÑA === */
  .mapa-wrap {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.3fr 1fr;
    gap: clamp(40px, 5vw, 80px);
    margin-top: 40px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .mapa-svg { width: 100%; height: auto; max-height: 56vh; }
  .mapa-pin {
    fill: var(--bronze);
    stroke: var(--bg-deep);
    stroke-width: 1;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 200ms;
    transform-origin: center;
    transform-box: fill-box;
  }
  .mapa-pin:hover { fill: var(--bronze-hi); r: 6; }
  .mapa-pin.active { fill: var(--bronze-hi); animation: pinPulse 2s infinite; }
  @keyframes pinPulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0.4; }
  }
  .mapa-region {
    fill: var(--bg-elev-1);
    stroke: var(--line-strong);
    stroke-width: 0.5;
    transition: fill 200ms;
  }
  .mapa-region:hover { fill: var(--bg-elev-2); }

  .mapa-side h3 {
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--ink-primary);
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .mapa-list {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px;
    max-height: 50vh; overflow-y: auto;
  }
  .mapa-row {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 26px 1fr;
    gap: 12px; align-items: center;
    padding: 8px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line-fine);
    transition: background 200ms;
  }
  .mapa-row:hover { background: var(--bg-elev-1); padding-left: 6px; }
  .mapa-row-pin {
    width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--bronze);
    margin-left: 9px;
  }
  .mapa-row-name { font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink-primary); font-family: var(--display); }
  .mapa-row-loc { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 9px; color: var(--ink-faint); letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; }

  /* === CASO SLIDES === */
  .caso-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: clamp(32px, 4vw, 64px);
    align-items: center;
  }
  .caso-img-wrap {
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 4/5;
    max-height: 72vh;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--bg-elev-1);
  }
  .caso-img-wrap img {
    width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;
    filter: contrast(1.08) saturate(0.82);
  }
  .caso-img-wrap::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(11,12,16,0) 60%, rgba(11,12,16,0.5) 100%);
  }
  .caso-content { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
  .caso-num-tag {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--bronze);
    letter-spacing: 0.32em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .caso-title {
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-size: clamp(32px, 3.6vw, 52px);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--ink-primary);
    line-height: 1.0;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin: 8px 0 8px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .caso-title em { color: var(--brand); font-style: italic; font-weight: 500; }
  .caso-loc {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .caso-desc {
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    margin-top: 20px;
    max-width: 52ch;
  }
  .caso-stats {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    margin-top: 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line-fine);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line-fine);
  }
  .caso-stat {
    padding: 14px 12px 14px 0;
    border-right: 1px solid var(--line-fine);
  }
  .caso-stat:last-child { border-right: 0; padding-right: 0; }
  .caso-stat-v {
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--bronze);
    line-height: 1;
    font-style: italic;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }
  .caso-stat-l {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 8px;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 6px;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  .caso-profit {
    margin-top: 20px;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    background: var(--bg-elev-1);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--bronze);
  }
  .caso-profit-l {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .caso-profit-v {
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--ink-primary);
    margin-top: 4px;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  /* === CASO COUNTERS === */
  .counters-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--line-fine);
    border: 1px solid var(--line-fine);
    margin-top: 32px;
  }
  .counter-cell {
    background: var(--bg-deep);
    padding: 24px 20px;
    min-height: 170px;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .counter-cell-v {
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-size: clamp(36px, 4vw, 56px);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--bronze);
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }
  .counter-cell-l {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }
  .counter-cell-source {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 8px;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 6px;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  /* === SLIDE 14 · PRUEBA SOCIAL === */
  .ps-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--line-fine);
    border: 1px solid var(--line-fine);
    margin-top: 40px;
  }
  .ps-cell {
    background: var(--bg-deep);
    padding: 32px 28px;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px;
    min-height: 200px;
    transition: background 240ms;
  }
  .ps-cell:hover { background: var(--bg-elev-1); }
  .ps-q {
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--ink-primary);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  .ps-q::before { content: '"'; color: var(--bronze); font-size: 28px; line-height: 0; vertical-align: -6px; margin-right: 4px; }
  .ps-meta {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  /* === SLIDE 15 · CTA === */
  .slide-cta {
    text-align: center;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .slide-cta .slide-inner { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
  .cta-h {
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-size: clamp(40px, 5.6vw, 88px);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--ink-primary);
    line-height: 1.0;
    max-width: 14ch;
    margin: 0 auto;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
  }
  .cta-h em { color: var(--brand); font-style: italic; font-weight: 500; }
  .cta-h u { text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--bronze); padding-bottom: 6px; }
  .cta-m {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    max-width: 52ch;
    margin: 32px auto 0;
  }
  .cta-actions {
    display: flex; gap: 18px; justify-content: center; margin-top: 48px; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .btn {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.28em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 16px 28px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 240ms var(--ease-out);
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .btn-primary { background: var(--bronze); color: var(--bg-deep); }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--bronze-hi); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .btn-secondary { border-color: var(--line-strong); color: var(--ink-primary); }
  .btn-secondary:hover { border-color: var(--brand); color: var(--brand); }
  .cta-foot {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    letter-spacing: 0.28em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 64px;
  }

  /* === RESPONSIVE === */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .bento { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); }
    .bento-cell.lg, .bento-cell.md { grid-column: span 2; }
    .bento-cell.sm { grid-column: span 2; }
    .dolores-wrap, .tr-wrap, .mapa-wrap, .caso-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .sol-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .ps-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .counters-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .metodo-flow { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
    .met-step { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line-fine); }
    .met-step::after { display: none; }
    .nav-dots { display: none; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .bento { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .bento-cell.lg, .bento-cell.md, .bento-cell.sm { grid-column: span 1; }
    .counters-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .portada-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="progress-line" id="progress"></div>

<header class="topbar">
  <a class="brand" href="https://www.surusin.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Surus · ir a surusin.com"><img src="./assets/logosurus-2022.png" alt="Surus · Desimplantación Industrial"></a>
  <div class="counter">Slide <b id="ct">01</b><span style="color: var(--ink-faint);"> / 15</span></div>
</header>

<nav class="nav-dots" id="navDots" aria-label="Navegación de slides"></nav>

<button class="nav-btn nav-btn-prev" id="navPrev" type="button" aria-label="Slide anterior (←)">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 18l-6-6 6-6"/></svg>
</button>
<button class="nav-btn nav-btn-next" id="navNext" type="button" aria-label="Siguiente slide (→)">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>
</button>

<!-- ============================== -->
<!-- SLIDE 01 · PORTADA              -->
<!-- ============================== -->
<section class="slide" data-slide="1">
  <div class="slide-inner">
    <div class="portada-grid">
      <div>
        <div class="kicker reveal" data-delay="0">Valorización industrial circular · Alimentación y Bebidas · España · 2026</div>
        <h1 class="display reveal" data-delay="1"><em>Valorización</em> industrial circular:<br>cada activo encuentra su <em>siguiente destino</em>.</h1>
        <p class="lede reveal" data-delay="2">Dossier C-Level con <b style="color: var(--ink-primary); font-style: normal;">17 casos verificados</b> de Alimentación y Bebidas extraídos del dossier oficial Surus. Datos literales — sin maquillaje.</p>
        <div class="portada-meta reveal" data-delay="3">
          <span class="badge gold">17 casos A&amp;B</span>
          <span class="badge">12 provincias</span>
          <span class="badge olive">5 subsectores</span>
          <span class="badge">PDF Surus oficial</span>
        </div>
        <a class="cta-top reveal" data-delay="4" href="#slide-2">Iniciar dossier</a>
      </div>
      <div class="portada-img-wrap reveal" data-delay="2">
        <img src="./assets/real/cover-portada.webp" alt="Cubierta dossier Surus A&B oficial" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high">
        <div class="auth-caption">100% Authentic · PDF oficial</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============================== -->
<!-- SLIDE 02 · 17 CASOS BENTO       -->
<!-- ============================== -->
<section class="slide" data-slide="2">
  <div class="slide-inner">
    <div class="kicker reveal">El sector A&amp;B en cifras</div>
    <h2 class="display reveal" data-delay="1">Diecisiete operaciones<br><em>verificadas</em> del dossier oficial.</h2>
    <p class="lede reveal" data-delay="2">Concurso, cierre de planta, sustitución de línea o desinversión. Surus opera como advisor y plataforma de subasta — Escrapalia — para desimplantar cualquier activo industrial del sector A&amp;B.</p>

    <div class="bento reveal" data-delay="3">
      <div class="bento-cell lg">
        <div>
          <div class="bento-n">17</div>
          <div class="bento-name">Casos documentados</div>
          <div class="bento-loc">Sector A&amp;B · 2008-2026</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bento-tag">Cifra del dossier oficial</div>
      </div>
      <div class="bento-cell md">
        <div>
          <div class="bento-n">12</div>
          <div class="bento-name">Provincias cubiertas</div>
          <div class="bento-loc">Sevilla → Araba</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bento-tag">Cobertura nacional</div>
      </div>
      <div class="bento-cell md">
        <div>
          <div class="bento-n">5</div>
          <div class="bento-name">Subsectores</div>
          <div class="bento-loc">Cárnico · Vino · Bebidas · Pan · Conservas</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bento-tag">Multisectorial</div>
      </div>
      <div class="bento-cell sm">
        <div>
          <div class="bento-n">5.059 m²</div>
          <div class="bento-name">Casalobos</div>
          <div class="bento-loc">Bodega · Ciudad Real</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bento-cell sm">
        <div>
          <div class="bento-n">180.000 €</div>
          <div class="bento-name">SADA-Nutreco</div>
          <div class="bento-loc">Subasta verificada</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bento-cell sm">
        <div>
          <div class="bento-n">6.000/h</div>
          <div class="bento-name">AVICU</div>
          <div class="bento-loc">Pollos · Stork PMT</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bento-cell sm">
        <div>
          <div class="bento-n">1.000/h</div>
          <div class="bento-name">Señorío de Molina</div>
          <div class="bento-loc">Conejos · Guadalajara</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bento-cell sm">
        <div>
          <div class="bento-n">5 M€</div>
          <div class="bento-name">Fricarne</div>
          <div class="bento-loc">Facturación 2022</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bento-cell sm">
        <div>
          <div class="bento-n">1.290</div>
          <div class="bento-name">Panificadora Baix</div>
          <div class="bento-loc">Clientes B2B</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bento-cell sm">
        <div>
          <div class="bento-n">1.186 m²</div>
          <div class="bento-name">Cuniporc</div>
          <div class="bento-loc">Matadero · Salamanca</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bento-cell sm">
        <div>
          <div class="bento-n">1.550 m²</div>
          <div class="bento-name">Domingo del Palacio</div>
          <div class="bento-loc">Nave industrial</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bento-cell sm">
        <div>
          <div class="bento-n">XS40</div>
          <div class="bento-name">Garvens PepsiCo</div>
          <div class="bento-loc">Controladora industrial</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============================== -->
<!-- SLIDE 03 · DOLORES              -->
<!-- ============================== -->
<section class="slide" data-slide="3">
  <div class="slide-inner">
    <div class="kicker reveal">Lo que la dirección general calla</div>
    <h2 class="display reveal" data-delay="1">Cinco <em>problemas</em> que ningún<br>C-Level dice en abierto.</h2>

    <div class="dolores-wrap">
      <div class="dolores-pull reveal" data-delay="2">
        <blockquote>El 80% de las desimplantaciones se gestionan como gasto. El 20% se gestionan como ciclo.</blockquote>
        <div class="attr">— Observatorio Surus · 2026</div>
      </div>
      <div class="dolores-list reveal" data-delay="3">
        <div class="dolor">
          <div class="dolor-n">01</div>
          <div class="dolor-content">
            <h3>Concurso de acreedores</h3>
            <p>La planta cierra por inviabilidad. Hay que deshacerse de todo — maquinaria, inmuebles, stocks — en semanas, no meses. Y el administrador concursal exige transparencia, no tratos de favor.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="dolor">
          <div class="dolor-n">02</div>
          <div class="dolor-content">
            <h3>Sustitución de línea productiva</h3>
            <p>La línea se reemplaza por una más moderna. Lo viejo funciona. Tirarla cuesta dinero y contamina. Venderla exige mercado, precio y gestión logística de retirada.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="dolor">
          <div class="dolor-n">03</div>
          <div class="dolor-content">
            <h3>Cierre de planta geográfica</h3>
            <p>Deslocalización, fin de concesión, impacto regulatorio. La planta entera (m², equipos, residuos) se convierte en un pasivo que lastra el EBITDA. Hay que convertirlo en liquidez.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="dolor">
          <div class="dolor-n">04</div>
          <div class="dolor-content">
            <h3>Reestructuración post-adquisición</h3>
            <p>Compraste una empresa concursada. Los activos heredados no encajan con tu plan industrial. ¿Cómo monetizas lo que no vas a usar sin destruir el valor de lo que sí conservas?</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="dolor">
          <div class="dolor-n">05</div>
          <div class="dolor-content">
            <h3>Desinversión con criterios ESG</h3>
            <p>El consejo exige economía circular, descarbonización, reporte no financiero. Tirar a vertedero ya no es opción. Necesitas trazabilidad de valorización industrial y segunda vida acreditable de cada lote.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============================== -->
<!-- SLIDE 04 · SOLUCION             -->
<!-- ============================== -->
<section class="slide" data-slide="4">
  <div class="slide-inner">
    <div class="kicker reveal">Tres servicios para tres momentos críticos</div>
    <h2 class="display reveal" data-delay="1">Surus no compra.<br>Surus <em>conecta</em> y ejecuta la transición.</h2>

    <div class="sol-grid reveal" data-delay="2">
      <div class="sol-cell">
        <div>
          <div class="sol-num">01 · ASESORAMIENTO</div>
          <div class="sol-name">Asesoramiento concursal</div>
          <div class="sol-desc">Inventario, tasación y plan de liquidación para administradores concursales y direcciones generales en crisis. Defensa ante el juzgado, marketing del activo, gestión de pujas, reporting notarial.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="sol-out">→ Activos maximizados<br>→ Plazos cumplidos</div>
      </div>
      <div class="sol-cell">
        <div>
          <div class="sol-num">02 · DESIMPLANTACIÓN</div>
          <div class="sol-name">Desimplantación industrial</div>
          <div class="sol-desc">Demolición recuperable, descontaminación, gestión de residuos, valorización. La planta se vacía dejando el suelo disponible para nuevo uso industrial, logístico o residencial — con trazabilidad ESG completa.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="sol-out">→ Suelo liberado<br>→ Trazabilidad circular</div>
      </div>
      <div class="sol-cell">
        <div>
          <div class="sol-num">03 · SUBASTA</div>
          <div class="sol-name">Subasta online Escrapalia</div>
